@MediTrack.MedicalAnalysisService.API_HostAddress = http://localhost:5188

### ── CLINICAL RECORDS ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### US14 — Registrar historial clínico manual
POST {{MediTrack.MedicalAnalysisService.API_HostAddress}}/api/v1/clinical-records
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "patientId": 1,
  "recordDate": "2026-06-01T00:00:00",
  "diagnosis": "Hypertension stage 2",
  "notes": "Patient reported headaches and fatigue"
}

###

### US14 — Obtener historial clínico por paciente
GET {{MediTrack.MedicalAnalysisService.API_HostAddress}}/api/v1/clinical-records?patientId=1
Accept: application/json

###

### ── STATISTICS ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### US18 — Estadísticas de cumplimiento de medicación
GET {{MediTrack.MedicalAnalysisService.API_HostAddress}}/api/v1/statistics/compliance?category=medication&from=2026-01-01&to=2026-06-30
Accept: application/json

###

### US18 — Estadísticas de cumplimiento de citas
GET {{MediTrack.MedicalAnalysisService.API_HostAddress}}/api/v1/statistics/compliance?category=appointment&from=2026-01-01&to=2026-06-30
Accept: application/json

###

### US18 — Estadísticas de asistencia a citas
GET {{MediTrack.MedicalAnalysisService.API_HostAddress}}/api/v1/statistics/appointments?from=2026-01-01&to=2026-06-30
Accept: application/json

###

### ── DASHBOARD ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### US16 — Tendencia de adherencia por paciente
GET {{MediTrack.MedicalAnalysisService.API_HostAddress}}/api/v1/dashboards/adherence-trend?patientId=1&from=2026-01-01&to=2026-06-30
Accept: application/json

###

### ── ALERTS ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Listar todas las alertas
GET {{MediTrack.MedicalAnalysisService.API_HostAddress}}/api/v1/alerts
Accept: application/json

###

### Listar alertas abiertas
GET {{MediTrack.MedicalAnalysisService.API_HostAddress}}/api/v1/alerts?status=open
Accept: application/json

###

### Crear alerta manualmente
POST {{MediTrack.MedicalAnalysisService.API_HostAddress}}/api/v1/alerts
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "patientId": 1,
  "severity": "warning",
  "reason": "Medication adherence dropped below 70% threshold"
}

###

### Reconocer alerta
PATCH {{MediTrack.MedicalAnalysisService.API_HostAddress}}/api/v1/alerts/1/acknowledge

###
